Petro - Canada raises posted oil prices . Petro - Canada said it raised the price it would pay for some grades of crude oil by C $ 5 . 00 / cubic metre or C $ 0 . 79 / barrel , effective immediately . The new prices were listed as follows : Edmonton light sweet C $ 175 . 00 / cubic metre , or C $ 27 . 82 / barrelCromer light sour C $ 169 . 00 / cubic metre , or C $ 26 . 87 / barrelHardisty medium C $ 134 . 00 / cubic metre , or C $ 21 . 30 / barrel ( ( Reuters Calgary Bureau ( 403 ) 531 - 1624 ) ) 
